@node "his" "History"

  @{B}  History  @{UB}

      Version 0.4Ô

        - Sprite collision enabled

      Version 0.3Ô

        - Fixed maths intructions bugs
        - Emulated all opcodes of Chip 8 (Except Super Chip 8 opcodes)
        - Add sound on/off option
        - Add Key to Joystick Option (only works in screen mode)

      Version 0.1Ô

        - Fixed the xor drawing mode original of Chip 8, graphics are good
        - Duplicated the window size
        - Add new opcode key VR

      Version 0.001Ô

        - First version released
        - Emulated 31 opcodes of 41
        - Emulated sound
        - Emulated very bad graphics
        - Emulated Input hexadecimal keyboard

